, depending only\non the topology, respectively, of the punctured or closed surface canonically\nobtained by gluing annuli or discs along edges of the ribbon graph.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Dec 2015 22:20:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2016 20:36:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2021 09:35:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-15"}
