ormalism is then applied to several sources with a mass around the\nfundamental scale, which are viewed as natural candidates of quantum black\nholes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Dec 2015 15:57:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-16"}
